channel.title: Nothing Happening
channel.description:
When I turn on my server... Nothing happens... I log on, it turns my screen black and nothing happens, I've tried multiple clients and they all do the same thing, I have tried everything in my server files nothing does anything. I had added a random event box, and it worked fine before that, I removed it, and had even saved backup of my server before I added it, my old and new files don't work... I am stumped on what I possibly did wrong... Any idea's?
(Ever since this Java update was available seems I've had this problem, could it be something with that? Not sure...)
